---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Reach out to Jon for speaking, advisory, or collaboration opportunities."
>
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container-page contact-panel contact-panel--single">
      <div class="contact-panel__copy">
        <p class="contact-panel__eyebrow">WRITE FROM YOUR CORNER.</p>
        <h2 class="contact-panel__title">
          I always enjoy hearing what others are building, learning, or thinking about.
        </h2>
        <p class="contact-panel__body">
          Share a thought, a story, or just a hello. I usually reply within a couple of days, sometimes with a resource,
          sometimes with a question, sometimes just to keep the conversation going.
        </p>
        <div class="contact-panel__focus">
          <p>If you’re reaching out, it’s usually about:</p>
          <ul class="contact-panel__list">
            <li>Finding more clarity and connection in your work</li>
            <li>Building systems that make room for people</li>
            <li>Practicing craftsmanship and care in leadership or life</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-panel__meta">
          <span>Prefer LinkedIn?</span>
          <a
            class="link-underline"
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonkohlmeier/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Send a note on LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-panel__socials">
          <p>Find me elsewhere</p>
          <div>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonkohlmeier/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/jonkohlmeier" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/jon.kohlmeier/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/jon.kohlmeier" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Facebook</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
